    "difficulty": "Intermediate",
    "whatItDoes": "A skill for working with shadcn/ui, a set of copy-paste React components built on Radix UI and Tailwind CSS. Components are added directly to your codebase rather than installed as a dependency, so you own and modify the source. Covers component discovery, installation via CLI or manual copy, theming, and composition patterns.",
